I just want to say thank you. The fact that you managed to bring a group of people together from different places, places that are angry and despise each other, is just incredible. YOU did that. Yes Theory did that. Love Over Fear, and Love Over Hate! I cannot believe that all from Los Angeles California to India and Pakistan and so many other places on the globe, you are changing lives. You changed mine too. I said yes to a year of traveling with my parents. I have seen so much, and I've grown even more. Currently visiting India, and I've been throughout Asia, Europe, Australia, and so many other places. I told my parents when they asked me if I wanted to do this, "Yes. Seek Discomfort." I might not have jumped into it if not for Yes Theory. Thanks for changing lives. (I'm from San Francisco, California so we're not too far apart.) :)
